    "This approach also improved the performance of face detectors.On the other hand, Reference [48] employed a Copy-Reduce-Paste method for data augmentation.",
    "This method increased the proportion of small objects, emphasized the importance of small objects in the loss function, and reduced objects larger than 32 × 32 pixels.",
    "Objects were scaled down proportionally until their size was smaller than or equal to 32 × 32 pixels.",
    "Finally, the augmented objects were pasted into the original images while ensuring that the overlap with existing objects was not too extensive.In conclusion, data augmentation is an important optimization technique in target detection algorithms.",
    "It aims to improve the generalization and robustness of the model by performing various transformations and enhancements to the training data."
